{"title":"献给每一个清晨","date":"2019-11-19T03:48:05.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Nov 19, 2019","L":"11/19/2019","MM-DD":"11-19"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/30/PXTlo4E2M73v1Km.jpg","link":"2019/11/19/献给每一个清晨","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.498Z","content":"<p>夜晚和白昼轻触的时刻<br>\n大地悄无声响<br>\n旭日轻缓地走来<br>\n把光亮和温暖带到这片大地<br>\n他来到温暖湿润的稻田<br>\n他来到寒冷龟裂的黄土<br>\n他来到河边婆娑的少女<br>\n他来到硝烟未散的战壕</p>\n<p>稻子微微拂动<br>\n黄土轻轻扬起<br>\n少女悄悄凝语<br>\n战壕里……</p>\n<p>死去的伙伴一动不动<br>\n在光晕下格外俊朗<br>\n火药余烟竟也肆意的迷人<br>\n野草在身旁静静生长</p>\n","prev":{"title":"草叶集","link":"2019/12/05/草叶集"},"next":{"title":"别","link":"2019/11/17/别"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2019/11/19/献给每一个清晨/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"},"reading_time":"133 words in 1 min"}